    <item>
      <title>印度大选意外：莫迪的失误以及接下来的走向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-election-2024-why-modi-bjp-s-lead-was-narrower-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在大选中遭遇重大挫折，他的印度人民党将失去议会下院的多数席位。莫迪表示，他将连任第三届，但人民党很可能被迫组成自十年前上台以来的首次联合政府。这使得莫迪和人民党在政治上的地位下降，因为他们败给了一个复兴的反对派集团，该集团通过竞选成功夺回了地盘]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-election-2024-why-modi-bjp-s-lead-was-narrower-than-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 17:50:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于以色列和哈马斯的反击，拜登结束加沙战争的努力受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hamas-rejects-gaza-peace-plan-without-permanent-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯跟随以色列，拒绝接受总统乔·拜登结束加沙战争的努力，双方都表示，必须满足各自提出的永久停火条件，他们才会同意停战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hamas-rejects-gaza-peace-plan-without-permanent-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:56:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪执政联盟险胜 8% 印度增长计划面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-s-narrow-election-win-will-make-it-harder-to-meet-india-s-economy-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党在选举中未能赢得多数支持，其雄心勃勃的经济增长目标面临风险，这使得他更加依赖联合政府来推动艰难的经济改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-s-narrow-election-win-will-make-it-harder-to-meet-india-s-economy-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊举行史上最长海军演习阻止俄罗斯石油输送</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/greece-deters-russian-oil-transfers-with-longest-navy-drills-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊海军在该国沿海附近的一片水域恢复演习，有效阻止了俄罗斯利用该地区进行油轮石油转运的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/greece-deters-russian-oil-transfers-with-longest-navy-drills-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法拉奇在英国竞选活动开始时喝了奶昔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/farage-draws-crowds-to-clacton-and-gets-drenched-in-beverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国脱欧的策划者奈杰尔·法拉奇在狂欢节般的氛围中发起了竞选克拉克顿议会席位的行动，数百人聚集到埃塞克斯海滨，承诺颠覆英国政治秩序。但并非一切都如这位新任改革英国领袖所愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/farage-draws-crowds-to-clacton-and-gets-drenched-in-beverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称有理由质疑内塔尼亚胡延长加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-every-reason-to-question-if-netanyahu-prolonging-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在周二接受《时代》杂志采访时表示，人们有理由得出这样的结论：以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡延长加沙战争是出于他自己的政治考虑，并且不排除派遣美军保卫台湾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-every-reason-to-question-if-netanyahu-prolonging-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 13:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪誓言即使失去印度多数席位仍将保住权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-poised-to-lose-india-majority-need-allies-to-keep-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党在议会中失去多数席位，但他仍誓言继续担任印度总理，这迫使他自十年前上台以来首次依靠盟友组建政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-poised-to-lose-india-majority-need-allies-to-keep-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
